  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become the hero of cleanliness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the POOBO universe, you are a tiny and cute poop trying to escape the toilet and survive! Fight against hundreds, even thousands of bacteria while creating the ultimate weapon combinations to claim victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Choose Your Character!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/f3b64e518ae2133adc5ccace4453b426.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/f3b64e518ae2133adc5ccace4453b426.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Equip Your First Weapon!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.poster.avif?t=1764605640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.webm?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.mp4?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of the game, you’ll need to make an important decision: choose your first weapon! Each weapon has unique abilities—some are great for close combat, while others help you defeat enemies from a distance. You can carry up to 6 weapons, so plan strategically and pick your first weapon to begin your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Level Up! Upgrade Your Abilities.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.poster.avif?t=1764605640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.webm?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.mp4?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve leveled up! Each level gives you the chance to make your character even stronger. Choose a card to enhance your stats! If you don’t get the abilities you’re looking for, you can reshuffle the cards and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Equip New Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/996fe28dfcf7dc4c10cec25fdd5856ac.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/996fe28dfcf7dc4c10cec25fdd5856ac.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can equip up to 6 weapons and 6 items at the same time. Each round gives you a chance to renew and upgrade your arsenal. Make the right choices to boost your power and dominate your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Upgrade Your Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/f17fa7bf1ddb15cdd72d70d76bfaeb53.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/f17fa7bf1ddb15cdd72d70d76bfaeb53.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your weapons and items in your inventory to increase your strength. To do this, you’ll need at least 2 of the same weapon or item. With each upgrade, you’ll grow stronger and gain an edge against your enemies!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to become the hero of cleanliness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In the POOBO universe, you are a tiny and cute poop trying to escape the toilet and survive! Fight against hundreds, even thousands of bacteria while creating the ultimate weapon combinations to claim victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Choose Your Character!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/f3b64e518ae2133adc5ccace4453b426.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/f3b64e518ae2133adc5ccace4453b426.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Equip Your First Weapon!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.poster.avif?t=1764605640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.webm?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/ebc4ecf322ffcf4a1fcc1bd12e4d11cb.mp4?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the start of the game, you’ll need to make an important decision: choose your first weapon! Each weapon has unique abilities—some are great for close combat, while others help you defeat enemies from a distance. You can carry up to 6 weapons, so plan strategically and pick your first weapon to begin your adventure.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Level Up! Upgrade Your Abilities.</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.poster.avif?t=1764605640\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.webm?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/c773dcaf66687f1499d4bd526a45bd93.mp4?t=1764605640\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You’ve leveled up! Each level gives you the chance to make your character even stronger. Choose a card to enhance your stats! If you don’t get the abilities you’re looking for, you can reshuffle the cards and try again.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Equip New Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/996fe28dfcf7dc4c10cec25fdd5856ac.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/996fe28dfcf7dc4c10cec25fdd5856ac.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can equip up to 6 weapons and 6 items at the same time. Each round gives you a chance to renew and upgrade your arsenal. Make the right choices to boost your power and dominate your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Upgrade Your Weapons!</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras/f17fa7bf1ddb15cdd72d70d76bfaeb53.avif?t=1764605640\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2989730/extras_big/f17fa7bf1ddb15cdd72d70d76bfaeb53.avif?t=1764605640 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enhance your weapons and items in your inventory to increase your strength. To do this, you’ll need at least 2 of the same weapon or item. With each upgrade, you’ll grow stronger and gain an edge against your enemies!</p>",
